\sum_{k=1}^\infty{\frac{x^k}{1+y^k}}=\frac{\psi_{y^2}^{(0)}\left(\frac{\log\,x}{2\log\,y}\right)-\psi_{y^2}^{(0)}\left(\frac12\left(1+\frac{\log\,x}{\log\,y}\right)\right)}{2\log\,y}
